Invocation Name: pico e. placa
des: In Medellin - Colombia, based on the car's plate last number, people are not allowed to take out their vehicules during certain times, from Monday to Friday. This Skill allows Medellin Citizens to know which numbers are restricted on each day of the week, or to ask about a number in order to know when it is restricted.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
